      "span_text": "That WT glycosylated CON-S gp140 binds to the RUAs of 2F5 in this setting is not surprising since we have previously published that CON-S gp140 produced in 293T cells (as the CON-S gp140 was produced in this study) is not glycosylated in gp41  ."
